    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="概述">概述</h2><p>Hexo 是一个轻量的静态博客框架。通过Hexo可以快速生成一个静态博客框架,仅需要几条命令就可以完成,相当方便。</p>
<h2 id="配置环境">配置环境</h2><p>系统环境： OS X / Linux / 类 UNIX 系统（我没使用 Windows 系统，所以不作相关说明）</p>
<h3 id="安装_Node">安装 Node</h3><h4 id="OS_X">OS X</h4><ul>
<li>直接下载 pkg 安装包安装</li>
<li>使用 Homebrew  </li>
</ul>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ brew install node</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<ul>
<li>使用 MacPorts  </li>
</ul>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ port install nodejs</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h4 id="使用软件包管理器">使用软件包管理器</h4><ul>
<li>Debian 系  </li>
</ul>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ curl <span class="operator">-s</span>L https://deb.nodesource.com/setup_5.x | sudo -E bash -   </span><br><span class="line">$ sudo apt-get install -y nodejs  </span><br><span class="line">$ sudo apt-get install -y build-essential</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<ul>
<li>Redhat 系  </li>
</ul>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ curl --silent --location https://rpm.nodesource.com/setup | sudo bash -   </span><br><span class="line">$ sudo yum -y install nodejs  </span><br><span class="line">$ sudo yum install gcc-c++ make</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h4 id="源码编译">源码编译</h4><ul>
<li>下载源码归档，并切换到所在目录</li>
</ul>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">tar -zxvf node-v5.x.x-linux-x64.tar.gz &amp;&amp; <span class="built_in">cd</span> node-v5.x.x-linux-x64</span><br><span class="line">./configure  –prefix=/usr/<span class="built_in">local</span>/node  </span><br><span class="line">make &amp;&amp; make install</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>其他发行版请自行 Google  </p>
<h3 id="安装_Git">安装 Git</h3><ul>
<li>OS X ：使用 Homebrew, MacPorts 或安装 Xcode 获得。</li>
<li>Debian 系  </li>
</ul>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ sudo apt-get install git-core</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<ul>
<li>Redhat 系  </li>
</ul>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ sudo yum install git-core</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h3 id="Hexo_的安装与配置">Hexo 的安装与配置</h3><p>所有必备的应用程序安装完成后，即可使用 npm 安装 Hexo。<br><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ sudo npm install -g hexo-cli</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>安装 Hexo 完成后，执行下列命令，Hexo 将会在指定文件夹中新建所需要的文件。<br><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo init &lt;folder&gt;</span><br><span class="line">$ <span class="built_in">cd</span> &lt;folder&gt;</span><br><span class="line">$ npm install</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>新建完成后，指定文件夹的目录如下：<br><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">.</span><br><span class="line">├── _config.yml  // 全局配置文件</span><br><span class="line">├── db.json  // JSON 格式的静态常量数据库</span><br><span class="line">├── node_modules</span><br><span class="line">│   ├── ...</span><br><span class="line">├── package.json</span><br><span class="line">├── public  // 公共文件夹，用于存放生成的站点文件</span><br><span class="line">│   ├── ...</span><br><span class="line">├── scaffolds  // 模板</span><br><span class="line">│   ├── draft.md</span><br><span class="line">│   ├── page.md</span><br><span class="line">│   └── post.md</span><br><span class="line">├── <span class="built_in">source</span>  // 资源文件夹，用来存放内容</span><br><span class="line">│   └── _posts  // 文章就放在这里面</span><br><span class="line">└── themes  // 主题文件夹</span><br><span class="line">    └── landscape</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>这个时候执行<br><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo server</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>正常情况下会输出：<br><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">INFO  Hexo is running at http://<span class="number">0.0</span>.<span class="number">0.0</span>:<span class="number">4000</span>/. Press Ctrl+C to stop.</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>这时候在浏览器打开 <a href="http://0.0.0.0:4000/" target="_blank" rel="external">http://0.0.0.0:4000/</a> 已经可以看到博客了！这标志着 Hexo 已经安装成功并且可以正常使用。</p>
<h3 id="部署">部署</h3><p>使用 Hexo 提供的一键部署功能，将网站部署到 Github 上, 在 Github 上建立与用户名相匹配的仓库，仓库名必须为[your_user_name].github.io, 硬性规定。<br>安装 hexo-deployer-git：<br><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ npm install hexo-deployer-git --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>然后打开 Hexo 配置文件，位置在 Hexo 根目录：<br><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ vim _config.yml</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>修改配置：<br><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">deploy:</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="built_in">type</span>: git</span><br><span class="line">  repo: &lt;repository url&gt;</span><br><span class="line">  branch: master</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>部署到 Github：<br><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo deploy</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>浏览器登录 [your_user_name].github.io，可以看到效果了。  </p>
]]></content>
